00:45:15.230 --> 00:45:16.700
Feel free to ask.

00:45:16.700 --> 00:45:20.380
&gt;&gt; That was good.

00:45:20.380 --> 00:45:22.030
Thank you very much.

00:45:22.030 --> 00:45:25.400
I mean that was very exciting
and it was an eye-opener.

00:45:25.400 --> 00:45:31.660
I wanted to ask you his painting
was primarily the landscape

00:45:31.660 --> 00:45:32.960
in rural areas.

00:45:32.960 --> 00:45:36.120
Did he do anything in the city?

00:45:36.120 --> 00:45:37.420
Did he--

00:45:37.420 --> 00:45:38.720
&gt;&gt; Layla Diba: Yes.

00:45:38.720 --> 00:45:40.020
&gt;&gt; Major cities in Iran.

00:45:40.020 --> 00:45:42.680
