00:51:17.590 --> 00:51:20.980
So, I'm still very careful
about what I say in terms

00:51:20.980 --> 00:51:25.990
of his later work and of all his
work, which is why this group

00:51:25.990 --> 00:51:30.200
of paintings which I could
examine personally and I know

00:51:30.200 --> 00:51:31.500
that the colors are right

00:51:31.500 --> 00:51:34.000
and the inscriptions are
correctly read and so on.

00:51:34.000 --> 00:51:38.390
But I hope very much our Iranian
colleagues will understand how

00:51:38.390 --> 00:51:40.790
important this would be
and they will publish--

00:51:40.790 --> 00:51:43.710
they're almost all in
the Golestan Palace.

00:51:43.710 --> 00:51:46.110
Some in the Malek Library,
which is nice,

00:51:46.110 --> 00:51:51.910
but they really need better
printing and it's 30 year--

00:51:51.910 --> 00:51:54.780
well, yeah, 1896, at least 20--

00:51:54.780 --> 00:51:58.420
1996 I think is when
